Package: gwasplot
Title: Modern 'ggplot2' Visualizations for Genome-Wide Association Studies
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Bartosz", "Czech", email = "bartosz.w.czech@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9908-3007"))
Description: Create publication-ready Manhattan plots, QQ plots, Miami plots,
    locus zoom plots, and novel genome-wide heatmaps from GWAS summary
    statistics. Reads PLINK, REGENIE, GCTA, and GEMMA formats natively.
    All plot functions return 'ggplot2' objects for full customization.
    Smart downsampling handles datasets with 10 million+ variants efficiently.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/bczech/gwasplot
BugReports: https://github.com/bczech/gwasplot/issues
